    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Most of the empty blocks are not intentional. In the mining procedure the Geth needs to prepare a mining block first, then do the PoW computation base on that. But the mining block preparation(packing transactions from the mempool) is not trivial which can 100-300ms. So in this time window Geth will push an empty block out first for PoW computation and then switch the target.\r\n\r\nIn the miner's perspective, the empty block is kind of the bonus otherwise the mining machines are idle.",
